    "description": "FinTech Global Incorporated provides various financial services in Japan. The company offers investment banking, including financial arrangements, financial advisory services, and consulting services on public accounting system implementation; documentation support services for public facility management; real estate asset management and aviation business, such as aircraft technology services, remarketing of aircraft/engines, and aircraft operating lease. It also engages in public accounting and public facilities management support activities; sale of public accounting software; consulting and system configuration, and operation services related to asset management of networked infrastructure; planning, design, configuration, maintenance, operation, and management of information processing systems for infrastructure and utilities; consulting for information processing systems, including data collection, recording, conversion, updating and management, and applied in database creation; and sale and rental of computers, peripheral equipment, communication devices, and software packages and services. In addition, the company engages in the real estate development, purchase and sale, exchange, leasing, management, agency, brokerage, and consulting services; internet-based information services business; and planning, operation, and management of websites. Further, it operates and manages a theme park. FinTech Global Incorporated was incorporated in 1994 and is headquartered in Shinagawa, Japan."
